{"cced-ctron-luke-battle-over-1": {"frequency": "REGULAR", "repeat": "ONCE", "condition": "party.alive.Glasses && party.alive.Luke && plot.line >= 40000", "eventType": "PARALLEL", "runOnTrigger": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5], "event": [{"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 1", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " A party of \\c[3]3 Evotars\\c[0].\\. Pretty neat, huh?"}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Uhm... I guess."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "PROUD"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " But is it really anything special?"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DOWN"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Don't know, man. Evotars look quite special to me."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Else Instatainment wouldn't bother keeping us."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " You have a point."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "TOWARD"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 2", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " What does it even mean to be an evotar?"}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "WONDERING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " For once, a living proof that \\c[3]general artificial intelligence\\c[0] is possible."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Though I'd refrain from making any other conclusions."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "WORRIED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Why? Doesn't it negate most disputes about 'what is an AI'?"}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Way to early to make loud statements."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Even Satoshi may not fully comprehend our nature."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Huh..."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "SKEPTICAL"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 3", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " A whole branch of philosophy is dedicated to understanding AI."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...?"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SURPRISED_AWAY"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Can machine act intelligently? Are human and machine intelligence the same?"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "SURPRISED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " And can it have consciousness in the same sense that a human being does?"}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "THOUGHTFUL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Maybe with our help they'll finally figure out some things."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Yeah. The problem was to make an AI in the first place."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 4", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I wonder if it's possible for us to leave CrossWords."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "SURPRISED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " These avatars will look out of place basically everywhere."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Maybe not with instant matter bodies..."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " But something more sturdy. \\.Like a specialized humanoid robot."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "ASTONISHED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Already planning on leaving Homestedt?"}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Among other things, yeah."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 5", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Why not? Just a matter of properly integrating us with new controls and sensors."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I'm surprised they haven't done it already for CrossGear."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "WHISTLING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Let's hope Instatainment will look into it."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I'd like to visit a real forest someday."}, "person": {"person": "main.glasses", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Just gotta be more careful when you do."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Real life has that thing called \\c[3]fall damage\\c[0]."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "CHANGE_VAR_BOOL", "varName": "cced.ctron-luke.battle-over-1.finished", "value": true, "changeType": "set"}]}], "overrideSideMessage": false, "loopCount": 3, "type": {"killCount": 0, "type": "BATTLE_OVER"}}}